                    output += '<td>' + val['BOARD'] + '</td>';
                    output += '<td>' + val['CLASS'] + '</td>';
                    output += '<td>' + val['SUB'] + '</td>';
                    output += '<td>' + val['PHASE'] + '</td>';
                    output += '<td>' + val['SEQ'] + '</td>';
                    output += '<td>' + val['CATEGORY'] + '</td>';
                    output += '<td>' + val['CSC'] + '</td>';
                    output += '<td>' + val['TOPIC'] + '</td>';
                    output += '<td>' + val['TSC'] + '</td>';
                    output += '<td>' + val['CONCEPT SEQ'] + '</td>';
                    output += '<td>' + val['CONCEPT'] + '</td>';
                    output += '<td>' + val['Corporate CONCEPT ID'] + '</td>';
                    output += '<td>' + val['WCRM CONCEPT ID'] + '</td>';
                    output += '<td>' + val['eCM Concept ID'] + '</td>';
                    output += '</tr>';
                    count++;
                }
            });
            let filteredData = '<h4> Total Number of Matched Rows ' + count + '</h4>';
            output += '</tbody>';
            output += '</table>';
            output += '</div>';
            $('#filter-records').html(output);
            $('#filter-data').html(filteredData);
        });
    });

    window.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function (e) {
        var myHilitor2 = new Hilitor("playground");
        myHilitor2.setMatchType("left");
        document.getElementById("txt-search").addEventListener("keyup", function (e) {
            myHilitor2.apply(this.value);
        }, false);
    }, false);

</script>
